パッケージ ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.model.entities

クラス StructureEntityVersion

java.lang.Object
ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.model.entities.StructureEntityVersion
public class StructureEntityVersion
extends java.lang.Object
A structure entity version consists of all SourceCodeChanges applied in a version of an attribute, a class, or a method.

For each new version of an attribute, a class, or a method, a new structure entity version is created.

作成者:
Beat Fluri, Giacomo Ghezzi, zubi, Michael Wuersch

    • getLabel

      public java.lang.String getLabel()
      Returns label for this entity:
      • In case of a class: 
         <className>@<revisionNumber>
      • In case of an attribute: 
         <attributeName>:<attributeType>@<revisionNumber>
      • In case of a method: 
         <methodSignature>@<revisionNumber>
      .
      戻り値:
      label for this entity.
